      "markdown_text": "=====================\n\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\n\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 100, 1280])\n\n=====================\n\n# Document of Peking University  \n\nX. F. [2022] No. 13  \n\n# Notice on the Appointment of the Administrative Team of School of Journalism & Communication  \n\nSchool of Journalism & Communication:  \n\nThe University has decided to appoint Gang Chen as the Dean of the School of Journalism & Communication at Peking University. Dehuan Liu, Kaihe Chen (with a probation period of one year), and Weijia Wang (also with a probation period of one year) have been appointed as Vice Deans of the School of Journalism & Communication at Peking University. Members of the original team will consequently be stepping down from their positions.  \n\nPeking University  \n\nPeking University (Seal)  \n\nJan. 4, 2022"
